Title: Smoky Mountain Christmas

reviewText: I would give it 0 stars if I could. Clearly everyone who purchased this DVD was duped into believing that it was the Dolly Parton TV special from the 80's. The seller should try including an item description as opposed to profiting from the many people who order this thinking it's something it's not. After the cost of return shipping this purchase was nothing more than a waste of my time and money.
summary: Not at all what it appeared to be
Title: Smoky Mountain Christmas

reviewText: Though I believed I was ordering another DVD with a similar name, this one is a treat. I gave it to my mother who absolutely loves it!
summary: A treat for the eyes and ears!
